data.description: AMAZING HOUSE AT EXTRAORDINARY LOCATION - close to Del Prado Blvd, Andalusia Blvd, and Diplomat Plwy. Everything is within a short distance like grocery stores, supermarkets, convenience stores, attractions, restaurants, and schools class A+. !!! ( NEW ROOF 2023, NEW A/C 2023, WATER SYSTEM 2020.  )Almost 2000 sq ft under air with 3 bedrooms+Den, 2 bathrooms, formal dining room, great room open concept, island kitchen, nook area and stainless steel appliances, laundry in residence, screened lanai, and garage for 2 cars. Tiles and laminate flooring, a master bedroom with a walk-in closet, and a master bathroom with a separate bathtub and shower. The exterior is a welcome to new owners with the cozy fire pit area, garden pedestal stands, and fence for privacy. This property is UNIQUE and it will not last in the market. Schedule your showing and make your offer!!!
